These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
3 different games are played: scrabble, backgammon, domino
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, train, jet-ski
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bongani, chaman
 1. the vegafina-smoker is the german##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is the mechanic##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person driving the train is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the designer is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person playing domino is the colombian##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
 9. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
10. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Game         | backgammon    | domino  | scrabble        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Transport   | train        | jet-ski    | boat       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Cigar         | vegafina     | bongani | chaman |

