House: cape-cod, townhouse, tower
The people use 3 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, bike
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the pony is the person driving the train##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the person watching disaster movies##1
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person playing poker and the person playing go##2
 5. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
 6. the person playing poker is the cape-cod house##1
 7. the townhouse house is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person watching adventure movies##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the tower house##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Game      | go   | scrabble    | poker         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure  | disaster  | animation     |
