House: ranch-style, victorian, colonial
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, weightlifting
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, november
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
 3. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
