 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the colonial house##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person eating strawberry and the person drinking 7up##2
 8. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the person playing domino##1
10. the engineer is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
