The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the dunhill-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person playing bridge##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person driving the subway##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Birthday      | october | july      | march      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Game   | monopoly  | canasta     | bridge |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Cigar         | oliveros    | dunhill | prince   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

