.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, goldfish, goat
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
House: farmhouse, cape-cod, modern
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, manager, musician
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, mousesy, september
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, ship, skateboard
1. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the musician##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the dressmaker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person who's birthday is in january and the manager##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the musician and the modern house##2
6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's birthday is in mousesy is on the left of the dressmaker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Pet      | mouse      | goldfish      | goat       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| House         | modern    | farmhouse     | cape-cod     |
