.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
City: paris, san-francisco, nizza
There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, amaryllis, dahlia
3 different pets are kept: hamster, mouse, cat
1. the owner of the mouse is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
5. the person eating peach is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the owner of the hamster is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| City      | nizza       | paris     | san-francisco         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Hobby         | photography | reading    | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | scientific | superhero    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Flower         | balloon-flower     | amaryllis | dahlia |
| Pet     | mouse     | cat       | hamster    |

