City: hannover, new-york, hamburg
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, dannemann, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person drinking milk is the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person driving the roller is the vegafina-smoker##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person drinking tea and the person traveling to hamburg##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
