6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the person watching animation movies##1
8. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
9. the french is between the person watching animation movies and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
